## Diagram Interpretation

- DPDCF does not belong to cryptographic, probabilistic, or simulation categories.
- It forms its own classification domain defined by:
  - deterministic execution
  - geometric operator fields
  - thermodynamic constraints
  - parity preservation
  - absence of entropy and randomness

